r":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"francobian33","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"francobian33","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://francobian33.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"francobian33","ctime_ts":1378581073,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/121411156/65344279","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18170490#t18170490","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18170490#t18170490","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18170490#t18170490","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_2058420","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://twitter.com/GeekFurious","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":18170490,"talkid":70978,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18170490#t18170490","upictitle":"GeekFurious: pic#121411156","article":"But read it again anyway. <br /><br />I've always wondered about your process of writing the earlier premonitions within \"Game of Thrones\" (like Bran's coma visions). As in whether you created them with future books in mind (or book) or if they were simply there and then became seamless parts of the story as it developed in your mind. This article leads me to the latter in that regard. Impressive.<br /><br />Your point about the third-person perspective is also helpful as I move forward with my own story. I'd actually been wrestling with a perspective problem and then read your words.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 years ago","ctime":"September 8 2013, 06:15:36 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Saw this last week","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://twitter.com/GeekFurious","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/twitter-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"GeekFurious","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_2058420","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=65344279&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"GeekFurious","ctime_ts":1378620936,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18171514#t18171514","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18171514#t18171514","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18171514#t18171514","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"palantek","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://palantek.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":18171514,"talkid":70982,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18171514#t18171514","upictitle":"palantek: pic#0","article":"Hey Grrm, i got a question in one of your interviews you said that you are more of a gardener kind of writer, that you put ideas into the story and wait to see what comes out of it. I have a question about that. Have you ever planned the faith of a character, and then in the middle of the story, when you were trying to get him were you wanted him to go, you realized he is in a hopeless situation and you thought \"Oh crap, now i have to kill this guy\" ??<br />Just something i came up with reading your Austinchronicle interview. I would also be glad to know if I have met such a character in the course of reading your books. Thanks anyway.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 years ago","ctime":"September 8 2013, 10:30:10 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Planning your voyage.","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://palantek.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"palantek","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"palantek","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://palantek.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"palantek","ctime_ts":1378636210,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18174330#t18174330","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18174330#t18174330","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18174330#t18174330","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_1232446","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"https://profiles.google.com/110046390189353308584","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":18174330,"talkid":70993,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/334458.html?thread=18174330#t18174330","upictitle":"Lula Longyearbyen: pic#0","article":"Now you are famous and rich. This changes the viewpoint of the most settled character. Success is a sweet but deadly poison for the unrelenting writer.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 years ago","ctime":"September 9 2013, 10:11:58 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Are you not scared that you have become a different person?","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"https://profiles.google.com/110046390189353308584","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/google-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Lula Longyearbyen","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_1232446","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=49953824&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Lula Longyearbyen","ctime